Investment objectives:
The project will deliver digital transformation for Queensland Ambulance Service (QAS) through the implementation of the Office 365 suite of products to augment the below enhancements to their current business processes.
19/12/2017,
19/12/2017,1. Undertaking smarter meetings; 
19/12/2017,2. Facilitating better administration; 
19/12/2017,3. Accessing information anywhere, any time; 
19/12/2017,4. Engaging and communicating better; 
19/12/2017,5. Supporting capability development; 
19/12/2017,6. Facilitating business intelligence; and 
19/12/2017,7. Enabling efficient workflow and approvals.

